02-15/ty-article/u-s-arab-countries-to-present-timeline-to-palestinian-state-and-plan-for-post-war-gaza/0000018d-ac49-d221-af9f-efe94e450000</guid></item><item><title>以色列考古学家恳求国家：不要在唯一发现的罗马军团营地上修建道路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-02-15/ty-article-magazine/israeli-archaeologists-beg-state-dont-build-road-over-only-roman-legion-camp-ever-found/0000018d-ac0b-d221-af9f-efeb7feb0000</link><description>现存的高速公路是致命的，但在哈米吉多顿的罗马军团基地莱吉奥（Legio）的新发现促使考古学家敦促政府：考虑其他方法来拯救司机</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 10:28:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-02-15/ty-article-magazine/israeli-archaeologists-beg-state-dont-build-road-over-only-roman-legion-camp-ever-found/0000018d-ac0b-d221-af9f-efeb7feb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对黎巴嫩南部的袭击造成十名平民死亡，真主党警告以色列“将付出代价”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/israeli-strikes-in-southern-lebanon-kill-eleven-civilians-local-sources-say/0000018d-abca-da6e-af9f-abcbb0fc0000</link><description>周三，以色列为回应来自黎巴嫩的火箭弹袭击而发动袭击，造成 1 名以色列士兵死亡，另有 8 人受伤，其中包括 6 名儿童。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 09:54:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/israeli-strikes-in-southern-lebanon-kill-eleven-civilians-local-sources-say/0000018d-abca-da6e-af9f-abcbb0fc0000</guid></item><item><title>即使与埃及塞西冰释前嫌也无法让埃尔多安在加沙立足</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/even-burying-the-hatchet-with-egypts-sissi-cant-get-erdogan-a-foothold-in-gaza/0000018d-a975-d0cb-a5ef-bb7f43580000</link><description>开罗是卡塔尔的主要竞争对手，无意将土耳其纳入外交接触的核心圈，而且埃尔多安能否拿出任何成果值得怀疑。 ■ 与有能力发表对抗性言论的土耳其领导人不同，塞西承认，开罗和耶路撒冷之间合作关系的重要性</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 04:00:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/even-burying-the-hatchet-with-egypts-sissi-cant-get-erdogan-a-foothold-in-gaza/0000018d-a975-d0cb-a5ef-bb7f43580000</guid></it